'''ló''' "(participle) by (someone)" is a [[Quenya]] word indicating the doer of a sentence after a passive participle. It is translated as "by" in English syntax.
==Examples==
*''[[Nahta-|Nahta]]na '''ló''' Turin'' "slain by [[Túrin]]"<ref>{{VT|49}}, p. 24</ref>
